OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773608768
OL,3,CChurch peregrine falcon killed by
OL,4,Cvehicle
OL,6,FAn adult male peregrine falcon has
OL,7,Fdied in a collision with a vehicle
OL,8,Fjust outside Romsey.
OL,10,FIt's believed he had dropped a prey
OL,11,Fitem and was trying to retrieve it
OL,12,Fwhen the collision occurred.
OL,14,FHe was born at St Mary's Church,
OL,15,FAndover in 2020.
OL,17,FThe bird of prey had come to Romsey
OL,18,FAbbey two years ago to mate with a
OL,19,Ffemale.
OL,21,FHowever, their nest was ruined by rain.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
