OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773608768
OL,3,CChurch peregrine falcon killed by
OL,4,Cvehicle
OL,6,FLast year they nested on the side of
OL,7,Fthe abbey in a gully and four chicks
OL,8,Fwere born.
OL,10,FKeith Betton, Chair of Hampshire
OL,11,FOrnithological Society, said: " Now
OL,12,Fthe adult male has died it is possible
OL,13,Fthat the young male will stay around
OL,14,Fto take his father's place.
OL,16,F"He is too young to breed until 2027
OL,17,Fbut if his mother is already carrying
OL,18,Feggs and continues to lay them, he may
OL,19,Fwell take on the role of a helper."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
